</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_548" id="273r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_548_r2l2">Dem edeln vnd veſten <expan>VVılhelm<ex>m</ex></expan> von <expan>Rechb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r2l3">von <expan>hohenrechb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> <expan>amptm<ex>an</ex></expan> ʒu Vffenheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_548_r2l4"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>amptm<ex>an</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Eberlein haſenneſts </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r2l5"><expan cert="unknown">H</expan>  wılden . Otten ʒynnagels vnd <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> hofers <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> der Jr ʒu <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r2l6">notdurft <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> bedürffet etc das haben wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r2l7">dıe <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex>werıkeıt</expan> <expan>ʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> der <expan>thumh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ʒu Bamberg vnd eẅr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r2l8">gütlıch <expan>abgıeng<ex>en</ex></expan> / das ſeͣhen wır ʒumal <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / Denn von der <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r2l9">vıer knecht <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> wır <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ ſıe oft gen vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r2l10"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>meltt</expan> ſein / wıe ſıe des reıchs <expan>ſtraſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / vnd dıe ʒu vnd von vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r2l11"><expan>gewand<ex>er</ex>t</expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . beſchedıgt vnd gerawbt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> VVıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r2l12">wellen wır Jn vmb <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> wıllen . vmb <expan>dıeſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>gang<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>handlu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r2l13"><expan>hıeʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> Oberſt ſchıerıſt keins argen <expan>gewarte<ex>n</ex></expan> für vns vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r2l14">dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> . Alſo doch Ob ſıe des Reıchs <expan>ſtraſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd dıe ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r2l15">vnd von vns <expan>wand<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd auch vns vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>daʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> nıht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r2l16">mer <expan>beſchedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_548_r2l17"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> v<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>kath<ex>er</ex>ine</expan> <expan>vırg<ex>in</ex>ıs</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_548" id="273r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Dem edeln und vesten <expan>Wilhelm<ex>m</ex></expan> von
                                <expan>Rechb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> von
                            <expan>Hohenrechb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, <expan>amptm<ex>an</ex></expan>
                        zu Uffenheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>amptm<ex>an</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Eberlein Hasennests, <expan cert="unknown">H.</expan> Wilden, Otten Zynnagels und
                                <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Hofers <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        der ir zu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> notdurft
                            <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> bedürffet, etc., das haben wir wol
                                <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu daz die
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex>werikeit</expan>
<expan>zwisch<ex>en</ex></expan> der <expan>thumh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu
                        Bamberg und ewr gütlich <expan>abgieng<ex>en</ex></expan>, das seͣhen wir
                        zumal <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>; denn von der
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> vier knecht
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz sie oft gen uns
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>meltt</expan> sein, wie sie des reichs
                                <expan>strass<ex>en</ex></expan> und die zu und von uns
                                <expan>gewand<ex>er</ex>t</expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> beschedigt und gerawbt
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>; wie <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> so
                        wellen wir in umb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> willen umb
                                <expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>gang<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>handlu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>hiezwisch<ex>en</ex></expan> <app><note><q type="date">oberst schierist</q>06.01.1423</note></app> keins argen
                                <expan>gewarte<ex>n</ex></expan> für uns und die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>,
                        also doch, ob sie des reichs <expan>strass<ex>en</ex></expan> und die zu und
                        von uns <expan>wand<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und auch uns und die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dazwisch<ex>en</ex></expan> niht mer
                            <expan>beschedig<ex>en</ex></expan>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> v<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Kath<ex>er</ex>ine</expan>
<expan>virg<ex>in</ex>is</expan>. </ab>
</div>
